    {
      "id": "graph-ref-smoke-instructions",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Test Instructions",
      "position": {
        "x": -430,
        "y": -220
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Graph Reference Embed Smoke Test\n\n1. Enable embed flag (`?graphEmbed=1` or env var).\n2. Confirm child graph renders inside the reference node.\n3. Set `mode` to `preview` and verify child is not interactive.\n4. Set `mode` to `interactive` and verify child is interactive.\n5. Confirm parent graph nodes/IDs remain independent."
      }
    },
